    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and value. This example exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved interior, reflecting a history of diligent care. It represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber automobile that performs with distinction. Contact our representatives to arrange a private viewing.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. You'll find it's been well-cared for, with a clean interior and a smooth drive that still feels great on the open road. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Come by and take it for a test drive\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera, featuring the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six engine and a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. This 996.2 generation example delivers 320 hp with the linear power delivery only a naturally aspirated boxer can provide. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension to offer exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row retrofit, and the rear main seal is dry. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, the cooling system is optimized with a low-temp thermostat, and the braking system features ventilated rotors with four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent stopping power. A true enthusiast's spec ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Service records available. Runs well. Minor cosmetic wear. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and reliability, having been meticulously maintained by a smoke-free owner. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, with only the slightest evidence of careful road use, and the body panels remain straight and true. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is supple with no tears, and the dashboard remains free of any sun damage or cracks. Every electronic component, including the responsive touchscreen interface and the multi-speaker premium audio system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, powerful engine that has benefited from consistent synthetic oil changes. The tires have significant tread life remaining, and the brake pads were recently inspected for peace of mind. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
