      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic refinement. Having undergone a comprehensive professional inspection, this model stands as a premier example of its class, offering the perfect balance of performance and long-term value. Its well-preserved interior and exterior reflect a history of diligent maintenance, making it an ideal acquisition for the sophisticated driver who demands both quality and distinction.",
      "price": 36800.0,
